; PRINT:; Resource Bindings:
; PRINT-NEXT:;
; PRINT-NEXT:; Name                                 Type  Format         Dim      ID      HLSL Bind  Count
; PRINT-NEXT:; ------------------------------ ---------- ------- ----------- ------- -------------- ------
; PRINT-NEXT:; Zero                                  UAV     f16         buf      U0             u0     1
